      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m finally ready to let someone else enjoy my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my 'baby'\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It drives just as smooth as the day it left the showroom, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It\u2019s truly a rare find in this kind of condition; I\u2019ve looked after every little detail so you don't have to. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and treated with respect, you\u2019ve found it. Let\u2019s get you into the driver\u2019s seat!",
